I cried a few times because I remember my first concert (*NSYNC no strings attached tour) I remember that feeling of seeing live music. If you know me you know soul is made up of music. I’d sing all damn day if people didn’t mind. 

My girls are the same…Music is just what our soul loves. I’ll never forget this and I know they won’t either.
